reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Loved these before, seems different than previous bottles?
reviews.reviewText: I have purchased these vitamins 2 times in the past and was completely satisfied with them. They were high quality and truly boosted my energy and mood. The third bottle I purchased in June ‘23 was not the same product. The b complex has a VERY distinct odor and taste that is quite unpleasant, but I’ve gotten quite used to it. The new bottle lacked that odor and absolutely smelled and tasted 100% like turmeric. I am quite disappointed not only because I feel I am out the money for the bottle but also because I very much enjoyed the last 2 bottles of the quality b complex I had purchased before. Have reached out to the company via their website, will update if they offer any help.EDIT:After contacting divine bounty, they sent me a replacement bottle and have offered a full refund for my original bottle. The customer service is outstanding. I am not sure what to make of things with the new bottle. The capsules are having a different effect on me than they have had in the past, not a pleasant one. I don’t know if the formulation has changed or it is just me. After smelling the capsules more, I don’t think they were turmeric, but they do not smell the same as my previous 2 bottles did. Could not be happier tho with the way I was treated by them as far as customer service.
